[🤩Islandwide Delivery/ Takeaway from Enjoy Eating House & Bar #supportlocalsg, at the comfort of your home 🏡🥡🥢]
Ain't my first time eating their local dishes and what's more it's @foodkingnoc approved 👍🏻Their dishes are created with a strong passion to present a heartwarming zichar-styled menu personally curated to Asian influences which makes Singaporean taste so unique 😋
•
They are currently offering both delivery and takeaway, and additional 25% discount for those who choose to takeaway! Whatsapp 92991601 to order and enjoy delivery service at your preferred timing to your doorstep islandwide! 🤗
•
Featuring 📸:
🌟🍜 Grandma’s “Te Kah” Bee Hoon ($12.80)*
🍗ENJOY "Har Jeong Kai" Wings ($12.80)*
🍲Hakka Steamed Tofu ($12.80)*
🥘Nonya Curry Chicken ($12.80)*
*Applicable to Delivery charges and takeaway container charge.
•
💌Thanks @enjoyeatinghouse for arranging efficient and fast delivery despite this period 👍🏻
#enjoyeatinghouse #sp #partipost #thehungertracklocalfood
@lunchingwithlandis Yass a satisfying feast indeed!! Aww thanks!! ☺️🤗
Wow what a feast! This looks absolutely amazing 😍
@foodwithtory.htx Yass we were so satisfied aft this meal! ☺️😋
@thevegetariancouple That's right, it's one of the best one out there ☺️😋

@frootlupe Thanks! Ohh u should try it soon then, highly recommended, esp their specialty te kah bee hoon 😋🤗Their Har Jeong Kai is not bad, worth trying! 😊 I've tried their fish and soup previously and it was great too 👍🏻
@thehungertrack Thanks for the recommendation. Appreciate it! 🙏🏻
@frootlupe You're welcome, anytime!! 😊 Lmk if you need the names of the specific recommendation dishes~
Great spread 🔥Been meaning to try their food for a while. Is their Har Jeong Kai any good?
@karhingc Yess their food is amazing! Ohh then u shld try it when u can 🤗 I liked their te kah bee hoon, fish and signature soup 😋👍🏻
@nycfoodcoop Totally, hope u could dig in with me ☺️🤗
@pigeats.balltravels Hehe thanks!! 🤗 Their standard is really good and gives u that homecooked feels 😋
